about.body.1.value: Hi, I’m Ana! By degree a psychologist, by heart a photographer. Based in Zagreb - Croatia, but available worldwide. I am not a person who likes to be in front of the camera, so at one point in my life I realized I like to be the person behind it. And ever since I become aware of that, I fell in love with the feeling.

about.body.2.value: Capturing moments and creating memories gives me the feeling of excitement and fullfilment. I am self-taught, but I began learning and improving my skills through various workshops and courses and I love that process. With my stile still evolving I am open to different ideas and projects and I’m ready to expand my horizons through photography. So if you have an idea, wish or vision I’ll be very happy to try to implement it, so feel free to contact me.

about.body.3.value: I’m a true fan of travelling nature. If days are free it means I’m on the road.

about.body.4.value: Camping is my way of travelling. Nature is where I feel at peace.

about.body.5.value: I can eat a lot of ice-cream. And watermelon.

about.body.6.value: I’m an introvert. Talking about myself is hard, so imagine how much time it takes me to write this.

about.body.7.value: There is not that many people who love sea and summer more than me.

about.body.8.value: I do yoga and I try to be regular in my meditations.

about.body.9.value: Little Eagle is my nickname because my surname in Croatian means just that! :)

home.testimonials.bovani.value: It was such a pleasure to work with you for my office photos! You're so pleasant to be around, and helped making me more comfortable in front of the camera, which is never easy for me. Thank you, I can't wait for new photos opportunities in the future!

home.testimonials.lucija.value: We are thrilled. Thank you very much for the effort and the whole agreement, our wishes and fast delivery. You have our recommendation! :)

home.testimonials.nikolina.value: There isn't a person who hasn't asked us who did our wedding photos - and we proudly and gratefully say @littleeagle. So cool, so professional, yet spontaneous and relaxed, just the way it should be. All recommendations from us - because Ana sees all the details, and the details make the difference ;)
